flowchart TD
  Internet --> LB[Cloud Load Balancer]
  LB --> Ingress[NGINX Ingress Controller]
  Ingress --> Frontend[Frontend API/UI]
  Ingress --> Auth[Auth Service]
  Ingress --> Notify[Notification Service]
  Frontend --> Backend[Backend Service]
  Auth --> Backend
  Notify --> Backend
  Backend --> Mongo[(MongoDB)]
  Backend --> Redis[(Redis optional)]
  Prometheus --> Frontend
  Prometheus --> Backend
  Prometheus --> Auth
  Prometheus --> Notify
  Grafana --> Prometheus
  Alertmanager --> Prometheus
